name: Zen Agenda. Scene 1.
description: Zen Agenda. Scene 1. They arrived here, in this relatively placid setting, not knowing how or why. The only thing they know is, they can’t stay long. An odyssey unfolds, rife with unfathomable phenomenon. Challenging life forms, intelligent and otherwise, are soon to appear. They must be dealt with - one way or another. Not one entity in this realm is neither malicious, nor benevolent. All of them however, are honest. It should be said, these “beings” these “animals”, as familiar as they seem, are not of our world. On occasion they will indeed do things that most of us would find rather unsettling. They cannot help themselves.
